## 表设计
### 学科表
学科id     学科 
``` 
CREATE TABLE `test`.`class`(
 `c_id` INT(10) UNSIGNED NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
 `c_name` VARCHAR(30) NOT NULL, 
PRIMARY KEY (`c_id`) ); 
```
![ER_CLA][CLASS]
### 老师表
```
CREATE TABLE `test`.`teacher`( 
`t_id` INT(10) UNSIGNED NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
 `t_name` VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL, 
`c_id` INT(10) UNSIGNED NOT NULL, 
PRIMARY KEY (`t_id`) ); 
```
![ER_TEA][TEACHER]
### 学生表
```
CREATE TABLE `test`.`student`( 
`s_id` INT(10) UNSIGNED NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, 
`s_name` VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL, 
PRIMARY KEY (`s_id`) ); 
```
![ER_STU][STUDENT]
### 学生科目表
```
CREATE TABLE `test`.`subject`(
 `s_id` INT(10) UNSIGNED NOT NULL,
 `t_id` INT(10) UNSIGNED NOT NULL,
 `point` INT(10) UNSIGNED NOT NULL,
 PRIMARY KEY (`s_id`, `t_id`) ); 

 ALTER TABLE subject ADD CONSTRAINT cyy CHECK(poin BETWEEN 0 AND 101); 
```
![ER_SUB][SUBJECT]
#### (2)写出查询每门学科各有多少老师的 sql 语句
```
SELECT c_name,COUNT(*) FROM teacher,class WHERE teacher.c_id=class.c_id GROUP BY class.c_id;
```
![图1][picture1]


#### (3)写出查询每个老师各有多少学生的 sql 语句
```
SELECT t_name,COUNT(*) FROM teacher,student,SUBJECT 
WHERE teacher.t_id=subject.t_id AND subject.s_id=student.s_id 
GROUP BY teacher.t_id;
```
![图2][picture2]
#### (4)写出查询每个学生各有多少学科的 sql 语句
```
SELECT s_name,COUNT(*) FROM student,class,SUBJECT,teacher 
WHERE student.s_id=subject.s_id AND subject.t_id=teacher.t_id AND teacher.c_id=class.c_id 
GROUP BY student.s_id;
```
![图3][picture3]
#### (5)写出查询学生名为 "Tony" 的学生学习哪些课程，以及对应课程的老师
```
SELECT c_name,t_name FROM student,teacher,class,SUBJECT 
WHERE student.s_id=subject.s_id AND subject.t_id=teacher.t_id AND teacher.c_id=class.c_id AND s_name='Tony';
```
![图4][picture4]
#### (6)写出查询学科“物理”成绩大于 80 分的学生名称的 sql 语句
```
SELECT s_name FROM student,SUBJECT,class,teacher 
WHERE student.s_id=subject.s_id AND subject.`t_id`=teacher.`t_id` AND teacher.`c_id`=class.`c_id` 
AND c_name='物理' AND POINT>80;
```
![图5][picture5]
#### (7)如果上述查询经常使用，需不需要创建索引，如果需要如何创建索引，并使用 EXPLAIN 对索引有效性进行分析
```
CREATE INDEX tname on teacher(t_id,c_id);//为教师信息添加联合索引

CREATE INDEX sname on student(s_id,s_name);//为名字添加索引

CREATE INDEX sub on subject(s_id,t_id);//为学科成绩添加索引

CREATE INDEX cls on class(c_id,c_name);//为学科名字添加索引
```
以上几项的索引选择性都比较高，索引效率提升较大

#### (8) 思考能不能去掉部分范式化结构减少表单数量，如果修改，修改后的表单对应上述查询如何编写查询语句，是否需要创建索引，如果需要如何创建索引，并使用对索引有效性进行分析

### 老师表
```
CREATE TABLE `test`.`teaclass`(
`t_id` INT(10) UNSIGNED NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
`t_name` VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL, `c_name` VARCHAR(30) NOT NULL, 
PRIMARY KEY (`t_id`) ); 
```
![ER_TEACLASS][TEACLASS]

### 学生表
```
CREATE TABLE `test`.`stusub`(
`s_id` INT(10) UNSIGNED NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
`s_name` VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL, 
`t_id` INT(10) UNSIGNED NOT NULL,
`point` INT(10) UNSIGNED NOT NULL,
PRIMARY KEY (`s_id`,`t_id`) ); 

 ALTER TABLE stusub ADD CONSTRAINT cy CHECK(poin BETWEEN 0 AND 101); 
```
![ER_STUSUB][STUSUB]

#### (2)写出查询每门学科各有多少老师的 sql 语句
```
SELECT c_name,COUNT(*) FROM teaclass GROUP BY c_name;
```
![图6][picture6]

#### (3)写出查询每个老师各有多少学生的 sql 语句
```
SELECT t_name,COUNT(*) FROM teaclass,
stusub WHERE stusub.`t_id`=teaclass.`t_id`
GROUP BY teaclass.t_id;
```
![图7][picture7]


#### (4)写出查询每个学生各有多少学科的 sql 语句
```
SELECT s_name,COUNT(*) FROM stusub GROUP BY s_id;
```
![图8][picture8]

#### (5)写出查询学生名为 "Tony" 的学生学习哪些课程，以及对应课程的老师
```
SELECT c_name,t_name FROM teaclass,stusub WHERE stusub.`t_id`=teaclass.`t_id` AND s_name='Tony';
```
![图9][picture9]

#### (6)写出查询学科“物理”成绩大于 80 分的学生名称的 sql 语句
```
SELECT s_name FROM teaclass,stusub 
WHERE stusub.`t_id`=teaclass.`t_id`
 AND c_name='物理' AND POINT>80;
```

![图10][picture10]
